properties.name: Thurston Hall
properties.description: Posted by EmlisThurston HallThe George Washington University\'s freshmen dorm. The cafeteria in the basement serves delicious food, never has the humble potato been seen in more iterations of the "fry." Blocks from the White House, across from the International Monetary Fund, Thurston Hall is in the middle of it all.
